<td bgcolor="#9D2EA8" style="font-size: 14px; text-align: center; color: #F5EFEF;"><em style="font-size: 18px">CALVERT ISD Coronavirus Update - Friday, April 17, 2020</em></td>
    </tr>
<tr>
<td bgcolor="#9D2EA8" style="font-size: 24px; text-align: center; color: #F5EFEF;">Calvert ISD will be CLOSED for the remainder of the school year</td>
    </tr>
<tr>
<td height="159" bgcolor="#9D2EA8" style="font-size: 14px; text-align: center; color: #F5EFEF;"><p style="font-size: 18px">           All district after-school activities, Athletic events, field trips, non-academic events and large getherings have been canceled until further notice<br><br>
      We will continue to provide updates through our website, district Facebook page and social media<br><br>
          Click <span style="color: #F90000"><a href="PDF/Notices/Coronavirus/COVID19-schoolclosure.pdf" style="color: #FF031B">HERE</a></span> for Update from Superintendent Dr. Thyrun Hurst , April 17, 2020 </p></td>
    </tr>
<tr>
<td height="268" bgcolor="#333333" style="font-size: 14px">
<p>We have created a special section on our website for detailed information about online resources for students and parents, detailed updates, curriculum resources and other information that will be helpful for our students and parents. Click <a href="Onlineresources.html" style="color: #FF0000">HERE</a> for information or you can click on the<span style="font-style: italic"> ONLINE <em><span style="font-weight: bold">RESOURCES</span></em></span><em><span style="font-weight: bold">/Coronavirus Updates</span></em> tab at the top of our website (Updated Tuesday, March 17th).</p>
        <p>Breakfast &amp; Lunch Information - Calvert ISD will provide a FREE grab and go meal from 10:00am - 12:00pm every week day at W.D. Spigner beginning March 17th. Click <a href="PDF/Notices/Coronavirus/GrabGobreakfastlunch.pdf" style="color: #FF0000">HERE</a> for more Information.<br><br>
          Lessons &amp; Curriculum Information - Parents will be able to pick up instructional packets also at WD Spigner from 8:00am - 12:00pm on Tuesday.  Parents wishing to view online Curriculum Guides  for each core subject taught may click <a href="PDF/Notices/Coronavirus/parent_access_information.pdf" style="color: #FF0000">HERE</a> for instructions and can also click <a href="https://www.teksresourcesystem.net/module/profile/Account/LogOn" style="color: #FF0000">HERE</a> to access the TEKS Resource System website.
          Should you need any assistance, please feel free to call our office at 979-364-2824.<br><br>
          Contact Information - It is important that we have current contact information for every student and parent.  If you need us to update your information, please click <a href="https://forms.gle/uKFYBg5H9vdN2QDk6" style="color: #FF0000">HERE</a> for a short survey.</p>
</td>
    </tr>
